        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-380",
        "content": "Jos, a little testy about his father's misfortunes and unceremonious applications to him, was soothed down by the Major, who pointed out the elder's ill fortunes and old age.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
