        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-380",
        "content": "She kept her own and became it very well.\" And his eyes filled with tears, which trickled down his furrowed old face.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
