        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-380",
        "content": "Amelia, as she read out the letter to her father, paused over the latter word; her brother, it was clear, did not know what had happened in the family.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
