        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-380",
        "content": "Having partaken of a copious breakfast, with fish, and rice, and hard eggs, at Southampton, he had so far rallied at Winchester as to think a glass of sherry necessary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
